  "label": "Sethran Wold",
  "description": "This individual is an undead human of cavern-wrought aspect, defined by pallid light skin stretched taut over sharp bone ridges. Gray eyes sit deep in hollowed sockets, and black hair hangs in long, unkempt strands that frame a jaw marked by old fractures that never properly knit. The mouth shows irregular, darkened teeth and a split lower lip fixed in a permanent deformity. Their manner is taciturn and sepulchral, speaking in sparse phrases and displaying a methodical, territorial vigilance typical of the dead bound to a single haunt.",
